OL,3,CBrexit vote 10 years on, how one night
OL,4,Cchanged Britain
OL,6,FWatch: A special ITV News programme
OL,7,Ftells the inside story of how the
OL,8,FBrexit vote drama unfolded on the
OL,9,Fnight, 10 years ago
OL,11,FIt has been 10 years since the Brexit
OL,12,Freferendum, which saw the UK vote to
OL,13,Fleave the EU in an unexpected turn of
OL,14,Fevents.
OL,16,FIn this special programme, the ITV
OL,17,FNews team, which was broadcasting on
OL,18,Fthat historic night, shares what it
OL,19,Fwas like as the results were gradually
OL,20,Frevealed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/3
