OL,3,CBrexit vote 10 years on, how one night
OL,4,Cchanged Britain
OL,6,FVote Leave won the campaign with 51.9%
OL,7,Fof the votes, leaving Remain just
OL,8,Fbelow on 48.1%.
OL,10,FOur correspondents reveal what it was
OL,11,Flike at the Remain and Leave parties,
OL,12,Fhow Farage's night developed and the
OL,13,Ftool which allowed ITV News to call
OL,14,FBrexit before anyone else.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
